        <p class="regular mar-top-24">Garment also does not collect information about the individuals receiving its services (“Program Participants”) nor does it make any information public regarding the Program Participants its serves through this Site. Program Participants are given secure, login-only access to portions of this Website in which only their first name is put into the Site and is viewable by the Program Participant. Any further information on the Site related to Program Participants is made only after a specific release has been signed and is on record with Garment.  If you are a Program Participant of Garment and wish to have your login credentials and personalized login-in portion of the Site permanently removed from the Site backend please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@garmentproject.org">hello@garmentproject.org</a>.</p>
